title: Whiskey Galore - Erin's Keel
description:
The band Whiskey Galore evolved in 1997 as a result of friendship and a deep passion for Celtic music between Mike Bowen and Kevin Briley. With the addition of Jeff Davis in 2002 this duo became a trio. Bassist Rich Spencer joined the band in 2004, making the band a quartet. We are frequently supported by the lovely singing voice of piper Kevin Briley&#039;s wife Kristin. The band is based in Bakersfield, California; their motto is "American Bred, Celtic Fed". Whiskey Galore&#039;s spirited brand of music has stirred fans in various venues in California and Nevada.

Whiskey Galore is a mix of raw and technical musical talent, blended together, producing lively Celtic music that can not be rivaled.
